### Test Generate Plan Function

# First, you need to get a JWT token by logging in
# Replace with your actual server URL and user credentials

### 1. Login to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}

### 2. Generate Meal Plan (use the token from login response)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/plan/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Weekly Healthy Meal Plan",
  "userData": {
    "age": 30,
    "gender": "male",
    "height": 175,
    "weight": 75,
    "path": "healthy",
    "activityLevel": "moderate",
    "allergies": ["nuts"],
    "dietaryRestrictions": ["vegetarian"]
  },
  "language": "en"
}

