# - The path field determines the type of meal plan generated
# - All requests require authentication (JWT token in Authorization header)
# - Validation will check age (16-100), height (100-250 cm), weight (30-300 kg)
# - Gender must be 'male' or 'female'
# - Path must be one of: 'healthy', 'lose', 'muscle', 'keto', 'fasting', 'custom'
